            Impact Portfolio
          </div>
          <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white sm:text-5xl mb-4">Case Studies</h2>
          <p className="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
            Detailed technical delivery breakdowns structured using the STAR method.
